---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="governance-score-card"
  description="Your Governance Score Card is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Governance Score Card is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your score card"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Governance-Score-Card-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>Answer the five governance questions, then match your results to the interpretation grid. Each property is mapped to risk level and a concrete next step.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/governance-templates-guided" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Fill the gaps</h3>
      <p>The score card shows what's missing. The Guided Templates show you how to build it.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">View templates ($5) &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/governance-implementation-guide" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go framework-specific</h3>
      <p>The Implementation Guide has step-by-step for CrewAI, LangGraph, and Pydantic AI.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">View guide ($9.99) &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/fit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Check your fit</h3>
      <p>A 5-minute fit assessment to see which services align with where you are right now.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Take the assessment &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your results.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
